{"tid":281023,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍城一人一個好食既餐廳","createTime":"2017-06-12T12:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T10:40:04.000Z","uid":43504,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5a3f7cba89d03bea6efa6b4f7dfe628bbe1fc29c","tid":281023,"uid":43504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"我真係諗唔到好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  想大家比啲日常啲既餐廳<br />\n<br />\n同心泰國粉面-鴨肉湯河幾好食 不過都少貴<br />\n<br />\n熱鍋泰國-幾好食得黎平<br />\n<br />\n仲有間係皇室甜品對面既泰國野（唔記得名）-地方好簡陋 不過啲野幾好食 價錢適中<br />\n<br />\n小方糖-咁多間糖水鋪算係有質素黎加上平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b11b78b07eabfdfac489fb71306d8f15b737113","tid":281023,"uid":11637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:02:30.000Z","msg":"求介紹 坐左廿鳩幾年都唔知有咩好食"},{"pid":"bc0d81ba9615495e1cb7b6c525be567e4622e813","tid":281023,"uid":11637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求介紹 住左廿鳩幾年都唔知有咩好食</blockquote>"},{"pid":"55d149e7978e59790ecbf66b44355eb5b73a812d","tid":281023,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:03:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求介紹 坐左廿鳩幾年都唔知有咩好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沙咀定壁屋呀 ?"},{"pid":"cbd8d28e8133b6b72736a9f4aabbfad3bafeb424","tid":281023,"uid":66639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:05:02.000Z","msg":"去親都係熱鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad314cfa317a2a4a1edca97498efb7017f670fa","tid":281023,"uid":112709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:06:17.000Z","msg":"泰風情都ok"},{"pid":"64f7f3a1b5b0