e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:50:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點睇台灣牛肉麵？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紅燒牛肉麵個湯成日唔熱㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我食過佢個二人晚餐都ok喎！係個魯肉飯重味左啲</blockquote><br />\n呢間OK<br />\n十幾年前覺得超貴<br />\n到而家好似無乜加到價咁"},{"pid":"36d2f35a60e09acebe78e4e70705dbfb9f032471","tid":281023,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:51:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清真牛肉館</blockquote><br />\n呢間又係做正<br />\n但我最愛係酸辣湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d534b70d0f9acc4db688f5be7647f7996b3c7b4c","tid":281023,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>清真牛肉館</blockquote><br />\n呢間又係做正<br />\n但我最愛係酸辣湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心覺得普通"},{"pid":"2b2bd84dd9a3333774c72fd994a7899f058ab5dc","tid":281023,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"泰金國點睇"},{"pid":"2981c7ec5ec1074faf6696941545d4d32f547a43","tid":281023,"uid":31321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:57:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蘭英印尼串燒 世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年附近讀書日日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正，個沙爹汁同雞脾黃飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a5d1c64004b95a5e1d7605553656b04093c14c","tid":281023,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蘭英印尼串燒 世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年附近讀書日日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正，個沙爹汁同雞脾黃飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識貨！<br />\n豬頸肉雞肉花枝丸都好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9676e9667cd0e999a3867324723620cadefe1b65","tid":281023,"uid":42454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:58:42.000Z","msg":"泰菜：隆姐價錢合理好味仲要送糖水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 泰金國冇乜邊樣唔好食 雞翼好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打冷：新城蠔仔粥好正 送綠豆邊糖水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n糖水：合成清心丸好撚正 地茂平之餘又幾抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點心：以前好撚中意點心居 樣樣野都食過 好掛住佢希望開返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家惟有食嘉豐 不過都係爭啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479f1db0f18bcfa0b1645a1d5edb6a3a6b79fe39","tid":281023,"uid":12264,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:06:49.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好吹奏？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幾間長期食開<br />\n唔想新假期拎料再推班港女去食<br />\n一旺左又排到on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：九龍城長大"},{"pid":"5a55e09775fb75b43bdf34b6a51caa2e55a8f8c1","tid":281023,"uid":107300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:07:23.000Z","msg":"興隆for sure<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09efa844fcc9ac0a7288880f8e0f7f23e6f54cf","tid":281023,"uid":10685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:18:25.000Z","msg":"糖水緊係口甜舌滑啦  芒果好正"},{"pid":"71155d7278d1c261b71c16205b4eed482b6713b1","tid":281023,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime