2c343635989caa2024f31e01a61eada31d","tid":281023,"uid":35431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T10:43:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食到生蟲"},{"pid":"524a6d7f8a6af2b3f73f70c592a0eab7fed23527","tid":281023,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T11:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>金豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食到生蟲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f6e9b6e880e636b8a5f421e02810098c9ced74","tid":281023,"uid":74897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T11:17:34.000Z","msg":"食京川、上海菜可以去九龍城廣場的江南，lunch都幾實惠！<br />\n食日本野去大助，定食60-70蚊，燒鰻魚都幾正！<br />\n食中菜去食得妙，食素去蓮花，清清地，款式又特別！<br />\n食泰國菜黃珍珍都好味，不過好貴。<br />\n食甜品我鍾意去小方糖，冬天食椰皇湯圓燉蛋白，好滋補！"},{"pid":"8c8702219ba9ad35cfbc6085f0c4fb2e8bd9e8c8","tid":281023,"uid":45094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T11:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b280c409ea07c22618180fde11933bae649100b","tid":281023,"uid":104669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:32:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃明記啲墨丸好正 打邊爐必買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔駛打邊爐 平時成日都買一斤返屋企分三次煮麵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗起就餓"},{"pid":"032a40cea11eeb2eecdcc344d53051c4fbeee0df","tid":281023,"uid":104669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食京川、上海菜可以去九龍城廣場的江南，lunch都幾實惠！<br />\n食日本野去大助，定食60-70蚊，燒鰻魚都幾正！<br />\n食中菜去食得妙，食素去蓮花，清清地，款式又特別！<br />\n食泰國菜黃珍珍都好味，不過好貴。<br />\n食甜品我鍾意去小方糖，冬天食椰皇湯圓燉蛋白，好滋補！</blockquote><br />\n黃珍珍好耐以前睇左段片<br />\n係明爐烤魚 一開爐就跳左勁多曱甴出嚟 <br />\n幾十隻啦 細細隻嘅<br />\n咁多年都唔敢搵返嚟睇  童年陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人睇過 係真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35976e3ba23c1d8a2f617ecbe8fcefe6fde19b33","tid":281023,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:39:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84d7090ae0f0584f9f2da64df086a5ecbffa809f","tid":281023,"uid":60858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T19:56:55.000Z","msg":"請問橙象好唔好食？我啲同事成日話地方乾淨又好食，心思思想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b7d16b176d9f43c572d37cef60c73ea7741c69","tid":281023,"uid":55228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T21:21:46.000Z","msg":"印象中海裕幾好，不過貴"},{"pid":"6f8235b5ea25c85150bf4dfe3108271e49528ae9","tid":281023,"uid":50024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T22:08:08.000Z","msg":"泰好味幾正"},{"pid":"4ae041282e1de3a69d1f127caf1fd21f37f94a06","tid":281023,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T01:40:41.000Z","msg":"啱呀   <br />\n人人去晒食小方糖合成地茂就啱<br />\n等我唔洗排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw有間印度野都好食  又平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f442d2acad35bf18d387aef9850381be1c3573","tid":281023,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T02:51:30.000Z","msg":"路邊街  船河屌打全港泰粉"},{"pid":"2103aae3d7342abcaaeeb82717604b33d0ee548d","tid":281023,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T02:53:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以唔好吹奏？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幾間長期食開<br />\n唔想新假期拎料再推班港女去食<br />\n一旺左又排到on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"h