normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幾間長期食開<br />\n唔想新假期拎料再推班港女去食<br />\n一旺左又排到on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：九龍城長大</blockquote><br />\n講呢句出來你會唔會覺自己On9?<br />\n唔會嘅話 你都真on9得可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事實班撚樣經常上黎拎料<br />\n你覺得你自己係咪on9呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你唔洗答，你根本係<br />\n新假期打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實間野唔係你食曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地推啲好野真係無所謂 大家欣賞<br />\n推埋曬啲紫薯雞煲睇都唔想睇"},{"pid":"60ff67de449c8dc5de6d9699aaa8ccf430e4633a","tid":281023,"uid":4006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"街市入面間泰國野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15bc8cdc227fd0023160ea95a324258af297586","tid":281023,"uid":74383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:09:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人打過牛精皇<br />\n啲料點樣</blockquote><br />\n新鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冬陰公湯底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4454e4ff73b7a9c6e4f0c9a208249ee98648f213","tid":281023,"uid":10142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:13:48.000Z","msg":"泰國嘢食開泰仔 泰發<br />\n糖水食開地茂 合成<br />\n打邊爐就一定方榮記<br />\n好想發掘更多好食既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242d1ed499145662e04bf60f2e1ae7124b5cddb9","tid":281023,"uid":55469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問橙象好唔好食？我啲同事成日話地方乾淨又好食，心思思想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每碟份量好少 同埋一入到去勁大陣酸粟味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係抵在每一日都有一樣野做 $1 優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415523c88ed9957ea6e977d19729219556c57c4b","tid":281023,"uid":10793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T17:52:10.000Z","msg":"越南麵包好無食？"},{"pid":"d9282b77db1ba86619c301b0d2d74380ef185ab5","tid":281023,"uid":41562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:12:46.000Z","msg":"淨係食牛肉嘅話，邊間打邊爐最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a758bba512279ea386f40e25634468a55065ba","tid":281023,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T05:58:38.000Z","msg":"清真依家仲好唔好食？<br />\n食過一次咁大把"},{"pid":"d4c89d3e7fe7fe86dd7a785edd43dae33eff201b","tid":281023,"uid":87363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T06:01:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲茶 我覺得嘉豐都幾正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD蝦餃裡面肉霉霉爛爛<br />\n蘿蔔糕試過完全唔熱上枱<br />\n咁你都話正？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前譚點(第一代)同埋點心居先至叫正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e89f194793556ae62f7ee6dfaf935fb6dd2bec","tid":281023,"uid":104661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T07:42:42.000Z","msg":"泰好味 同 金蘭花 都唔錯<br />\n橙象垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n泰金國都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n清真牛肉館 打鼓嶺道果間唔錯<br />\n新城都好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n合城差過地茂<br />\n嘉豐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f622fcfe33c2dc8dd0eb05c7be273e31c312ef","tid":281023,"uid":74392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T07:47:08.000Z","msg":"興隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35912f9a331a7c158596be76a31d56d871ad99b5","tid":281023,"uid":87363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:27:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>興隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抵食地道之選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc008c7a1d65b7b397d7d0554058ff7d9d80c3a9","tid":281023,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:32:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"991da197e1fbe54d69641db7cd55e44300028560","tid":281023,"uid":54787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:32:28.000Z","msg":"聽連登仔講去隆姐食<br />\n<br />\n同出面一樣50蚊到又無野飲份量又少，個糖水係細碗仔涼粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本水9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c228a4ae30595d972357c6c3a36088ac9ca0f7","tid":281023,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:37:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>德昌</blockquote><br />\n呢間oK<br />\n不過好似無土瓜灣果時咁出色</blockquote><br />\n辣椒油好得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正呀</blockquote><br />\n墨丸河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bbd23242c3ae4d9d8dc520b6f7be4e5b8973baf","tid":281023,"uid":1585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:40:31.000Z","msg":"金泰"},{"pid":"c4341668e41bf99825eff5bb97c6c99289dafac6","tid":281023,"uid":1585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:41:37.000Z","msg":"仲有小店"},{"pid":"f365dc8f0c93fd6a91f478cb86fbf37286278c24","tid":281023,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃明記啲墨丸好正 打邊爐必買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲火龍果仲正呀"},{"pid":"45ab0432d9e4708f595c6cb38277d325eeff3417","tid":281023,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:30:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黃明記啲墨丸好正 打邊爐必買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲火龍果仲正呀</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/18/233008_b16bd210753ab351e443a3a19f011f6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2F233008_b16bd210753ab351e443a3a19f011f6a.jpg&h=d11933c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffee98e5d35212700ac03b744857fa75fef94092","tid":281023,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T18:53:19.000Z","msg":"南記，全香港最好食嘅潮洲菜，沒有之一。<br />\n<br />\n泰國野泰風情係我覺得咁多間最高質，個炒金邊粉無得輸。<br />\n聯發個叉燒蛋飯係貴啲但啲蛋真係好滑叉燒真係好正，加杯奶茶真係無得彈。<br />\n義香豆品所有野都好食，成日食三寶撈米大菜糕，韮菜餅好食但唔係成日有。<br />\n豆腐花始終愛公和，個三寶魚蛋係超滑！<br />\n<br />\n麵包福佬村道間Ceres真係好香好好食，不過好貴我淨係幫親得起白麵包同提子包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n豪華酥皮蛋撻係全香港最撚好食！"}]}